# Pomodoro_App
 creating a promodoro app (A famous technique that helps people time manage and finish tasks).

The Pomodoro Technique breakdown:
1) Decide on the task to be done.
2) Set the timer to 25 mins.
3) Work on the task until the timer rings.
4) Take a short 5 minute break.
    The program will repeat steps 1-4, 4 times.
5) Take a 15-30 minute break.


Building a Project that will help the user to manage their time better.